<i>noun</i>: 건축학 [건ː추칵], 건축 [건ː축] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>건축학 [건ː추칵]</dt><br>
<dd>architecture; construction engineering</dd><br>
<dd>건축에 관한 이론과 기술, 또는 예술로서의 건축을 연구하는 학문.</dd><br>
<dd>An academic discipline that studies architectural theories and technology or architecture as an art.</dd><br>
<dt>건축 [건ː축]</dt><br>
<dd>architecture; construction; building</dd><br>
<dd>집이나 건물, 다리 등을 설계하여 지음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of designing and constructing houses, buildings, bridges, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>